OL,3,CScotland supporters to pack fanzones
OL,4,Cand pubs for first World Cup game
OL,6,FScotland fans across the country are
OL,7,Fpreparing for the national team's
OL,8,Freturn to World Cup football, with
OL,9,Ffanzones, pubs and other venues
OL,10,Fexpected to be packed.
OL,12,FSteve Clarke's men will take on Haiti
OL,13,Fin their opening fixture in the US,
OL,14,Fwith kick-off at 2am on Sunday, UK
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
