OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781384337
OL,3,CScotland supporters to pack fanzones
OL,4,Cand pubs for first World Cup game
OL,6,FThe late-night kick-offs for
OL,7,FScotland's group stage games means
OL,8,Fthat most councils around the country
OL,9,Fhave chosen to allow extended
OL,10,Flicensing hours for pubs and other
OL,11,Fvenues.
OL,13,FThe hospitality trade expects to see a
OL,14,Fsales boost of about 40% in pubs and
OL,15,Fbars.
OL,17,FMonday, June 15 will be a bank holiday
OL,18,Fto mark the occasion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
