FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781384337
OL,3,CScotland supporters to pack fanzones
OL,4,Cand pubs for first World Cup game
OL,6,FThe Ovo Hydro arena in Glasgow says it
OL,7,Fwill host Scotland's largest fan zone,
OL,8,Fwith doors opening at 10pm on Saturday
OL,9,Fahead of the Scotland v Haiti game.
OL,11,FThere will be a programme of music,
OL,12,Fentertainment and punditry before fans
OL,13,Fwatch the match on a 20-metre screen.
OL,15,FThousands of Tartan Army members are
OL,16,Fexpected to attend the Hydro during
OL,17,FScotland's group stage fixtures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781384337
OL,3,CScotland supporters to pack fanzones
OL,4,Cand pubs for first World Cup game
OL,6,FDominic McKay, chief executive of the
OL,7,FSEC, which includes the Hydro arena,
OL,8,Fsaid earlier: "This summer will be a
OL,9,Fmoment that lives beyond football and
OL,10,Fone of real national significance.
OL,12,F"The stage is now set for an
OL,13,Funforgettable series of events where
OL,14,Fsupporters can come together as the
OL,15,Fdrama unfolds in the United States."
OL,26,@pD@OOUtD@AOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
