OL,3,CScotland supporters to pack fanzones
OL,4,Cand pubs for first World Cup game
OL,6,FPaul Togneri, from the Scottish Beer
OL,7,Fand Pub Association, said: "Even with
OL,8,Fa 2am kick-off, Scotland at a World
OL,9,FCup for the first time in 28 years is
OL,10,Fa huge draw and pubs will still be
OL,11,Fbusy as fans come together to cheer on
OL,12,Fthe team.
OL,14,F"An extra 120,000 pints, worth
OL,15,F#600,000, underlines just how
OL,16,Fimportant these moments are for pubs
OL,17,Fand brewers alike.
OL,26,@oD@\OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
