FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781384337
OL,3,CScotland supporters to pack fanzones
OL,4,Cand pubs for first World Cup game
OL,6,F"There's simply no better place to
OL,7,Fwatch Scotland than in your local `
OL,8,Fsharing the atmosphere, the passion
OL,9,Fand the occasion with fellow fans."
OL,11,FSome Scottish institutions have also
OL,12,Fchosen to temporarily rebrand
OL,13,Fthemselves to honour the World Cup
OL,14,Fsquad.
OL,16,FEast Renfrewshire Council is renaming
OL,17,Fitself "East Robbo-shire Council"
OL,18,Fafter captain Andy Robertson.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@cO]yD@HOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
