OL,3,CScotland supporters to pack fanzones
OL,4,Cand pubs for first World Cup game
OL,6,FA McGill's bus is becoming "McGinn's"
OL,7,Fin tribute to midfield favourite John
OL,8,FMcGinn.
OL,10,FFirst Minister John Swinney said: "As
OL,11,Fwe head into this weekend, I want to
OL,12,Fremind everyone to enjoy themselves
OL,13,Fresponsibly and safely.
OL,15,F"For those lucky enough to travel to
OL,16,Fthe US, please remember to check and
OL,17,Ffollow FCDO (Foreign, Commonwealth &
OL,18,FDevelopment Office) advice.
OL,20,F"Come on Scotland. The world is
OL,21,Fwatching. Let's make history."
OL,26,@nD@\OUnD@eO]rD@cOUwD@AOU|D@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
