OL,3,CScotland supporters to pack fanzones
OL,4,Cand pubs for first World Cup game
OL,6,FScottish Secretary Douglas Alexander
OL,7,Fsaid: "The very best of luck to Steve
OL,8,FClarke's squad as they kick off in
OL,9,FBoston this weekend.
OL,11,F"Seeing Scotland playing in a World
OL,12,FCup is a moment for every fan to
OL,13,Fcherish ` we have waited a long time
OL,14,Ffor it.
OL,16,F"I'll be cheering on the team as they
OL,17,Ftake on the world's best. I know the
OL,18,Fentire nation will be right behind
OL,19,Fthem."
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
