OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781384337
OL,3,CScotland supporters to pack fanzones
OL,4,Cand pubs for first World Cup game
OL,6,FPolice Scotland Chief Superintendent
OL,7,FNeil MacDougall previously said:
OL,8,F"Police Scotland's role will be to act
OL,9,Fas a liaison for travelling Scotland
OL,10,Ffans at the World Cup and support
OL,11,Fevent organisers in this country with
OL,12,Fsafety advice at fan zones.
OL,14,F"For Scotland fans travelling to the
OL,15,FWorld Cup, engagement and cooperation
OL,16,Fwith local police will help make it an
OL,17,Fenjoyable trip. Visit the Foreign,
OL,18,FCommonwealth and Development Office
OL,19,Fwebsite for useful advice on travel
OL,20,Fand passports.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
