OL,3,CScotland supporters to pack fanzones
OL,4,Cand pubs for first World Cup game
OL,6,F"For people visiting fan zones in
OL,7,FScotland, we are encouraging the
OL,8,Fpublic to trust their instincts and
OL,9,Freport anything that doesn't feel
OL,10,Fright to security or the police."
